

This directory includes all idl .pro routines written for mir.

These routines are named with prefixes describing a few broad categories :

cal_ : Calibration routines used in common w/ bas,gai,pas,wlm
dat_ : Data manipulation for idl mir structures  
dbi_ : Database interaction
fil_ : Host file manipulation
gai_ : Gain calibration
pas_ : Passband calibration
plo_ : Plotting 
pri_ : Printing 
pro_ : Programming 
rep_ : Reports 
uti_ : Small utility programs
wlm_ : Water line monitor
 
